Check this post or our video in our YouTube Channel for full coverage:

• Camera
• Design & Specs
• Portrait Video

• Battery Life

ProRes 4K/30fps is also coming later this year and requires an iPhone with at least 256GBs (128GB versions are capped at ProRes 1080p/30fps).

The storage options have also been increased since Apple added a new 1TB variant.
